i-MSCP RemoteBridge plugin ChangeLog
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    - Update: Updated to i-MSCP >= 1.2.17 -> API >= 1.0.0	
	- Fix: most actions are not working
	- Fix: some 'Undefined index' notices
    - Added: Add, edit and delete DNS records
	
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.10 (internal release)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    - Added: actions for add, edit and delete FTP accounts
    - Added: actions for edit and delete mail accounts
    - code cleanup	
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.9
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    - Added: action 'get_mail' which creates a list of a users mailaccounts
	- Renamed: actions are renamed to bring more clarity in the name i.e. suspend_dmn, terminate_dmn ...

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.8
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    - Fixed: Domain update was not working with Domains created by i-MSCP Panel
	- update is now only updating domain related things
	- removed unneded code for updating user details
	- action renamed to update_dmn
	- Renamed: action for adding mails are now 'add_mail'

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.7
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    - Added: Add mailaccount for mailbox and/or forwarding
		- action 'addmail'
	
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.6
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	- Added: User list 
	- action 'get_dmn'

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.5
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	- Added: Update user and domain
	- action 'update'

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.4
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	- Fixed: Disabled items must not be counted by the getCountRequests() method
	
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.3
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	- Fixed: Column domain_created_id has been removed from i-MSCP core

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	- Small fixes

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

2013-11-18: Sascha Bay
	- RELEASE i-MSCP RemoteBridge plugin 0.0.1
